# **LSTM Forecasting**

This directory contains **Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) based time-series forecasting projects**. LSTM is a type of recurrent neural network (RNN) designed to handle long-term dependencies in sequential data, making it well-suited for **time-series forecasting**.

